{"tid":2370022,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都好攰","createTime":"2021-01-17T16:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T08:38:25.000Z","uid":124514,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7145d767a0956bbed639084a24f25474fb60db69","tid":2370022,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"有冇人成日都好似提唔起精神<br />\n除左起身嗰下清醒啲之外<br />\n一返工搭車嗰陣又開始好攰<br />\n恰下恰下好眼訓<br />\n<br />\n就算放假<br />\n一個人去散步定行商場都好<br />\n行一陣都好攰好攰<br />\n睇嘢好似好迷幻<br />\n集中唔到<br />\nout哂fo<br />\n好似喺夢境咁<br />\n<br />\n想知有冇人都會咁？<br />\n係生活上太多嘅無力感會令我咁嗎？<br />\n我記得以前我都唔會有呢種情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d91c57a98be0e88146b5e6f3f33de4476aece2","tid":2370022,"uid":304619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:21:44.000Z","msg":"以為自己開po 呢幾年就開始係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放緊大假都係咁攰"},{"pid":"4ad6dea8d43032fb9987c8cb30ff76b5a9e6ac13","tid":2370022,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:26:14.000Z","msg":"打少啲丁"},{"pid":"f68274f10c08e1f88058f86e4cb13267a9eb8a6c","tid":2370022,"uid":124514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"41d91c57a98be0e88146b5e6f3f33de4476aece2","tid":2370022,"uid":304619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:21:44.000Z","msg":"以為自己開po 呢幾年就開始係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放緊大假都係咁攰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"絲係咪同我一樣冇目標冇方向冇將來感到絕望<br />\n我做緊一份自己唔鐘意嘅工<br />\n呢啲時勢走左又驚揾唔到工一年半載<br />\n放工好攰又冇心機揾工<br />\n日日都係矛盾當中"},{"pid":"e505616ca2794d7a66e9fd854b634ca3c6ccc8e2","tid":2370022,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ad6dea8d43032fb9987c8cb30ff76b5a9e6ac13","tid":2370022,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:26:14.000Z","msg":"打少啲丁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"絲黎架<